We are looking for a Training Assistant who would be directly reporting to the head of training department. To thrive in this role you must have passion for training and must have well- developed technical skills, professional skills and interpersonal skills that can be translated into effective training. Person must have sound presentation skills, knowledge of adult learning theories and training methodologies.
Job Specification
Basic Requirements:
• Graduate/Masters
• Excellent communication skills
• Prior experience in training
• Must be willing to work in Night Shift
• Males Only
Should have
• Intellectual abilities to synthesize evaluate and communicate ideas.
• Effective Interpersonal skills that facilitate two way communication
• Positive attitude
• Must have sound knowledge of Training methodologies and techniques.
